snippet.title: Max Payne Kung Fu 3.0
snippet.description:
An old video showing off some random moves in the Kung Fu mod made by Kenneth Yeung for the PC version of Max Payne.

More info can be found at: http://web.archive.org/web/20030407180818/http://kungfu.maxpayneheadquarters.com/kungfu.html

Possibly easier to read mirror:
https://sites.google.com/site/mrpyide/maxpaynekungfu3.0guide
